# Local scan output — each contributor regenerates this against their own
# workspace via `make scan /path`; not meant to be shared in git. The
# whole scans/ subfolder is ignored (one JSON per scanned folder, plus
# the auto-generated index.json the viewer reads at boot).
viewer/public/fixtures/scans/
# Legacy single-file path from before the per-folder scans/ layout; left
# here so old workspaces don't accidentally commit a stale custom.json.
viewer/public/fixtures/custom.json

# Kotlin/Gradle fixture build artifacts — Gradle creates `.gradle/`
# (caches, daemon state, lockfiles) and `build/` (compiled classes,
# generated sources) on every invocation. Both are reproducible from
# the fixture sources and shouldn't be tracked.
tests/fixtures/kotlin-ktor/.gradle/
tests/fixtures/kotlin-ktor/build/
